            "notes": "This Control deck focuses on using a variety of counterspells, removal spells, and disruptive creatures to control the opponent's board and prevent them from executing their game plan effectively. With Ertai Resurrected as the commander, the deck also aims to gradually accumulate resources and outvalue opponents with card advantage. The deck contains a mix of efficient removal like Fatal Push and Drown in the Loch, versatile counterspells like Cryptic Command and Force of Negation, and powerful card draw options like Mystic Confluence and Brainstorm. By disrupting the opponent's plays and generating incremental advantages over time, this deck aims to outmaneuver opponents and secure victory through attrition and resource management."
